---
title: Toscana Tortelloni Vegetable Soup All In One Pot
description: As the temperature continues to drop, we find ourselves craving the culinary equivalent of a cozy blanket. Enter: this hearty, soul-warming soup. It’s chock full of goodness—that is to say carrot, onion, diced tomatoes, tender cheese tortelloni, and a sprinkle of Parm. And because no good brothy bowl is complete without some carbs for dunking, we’re also throwing in a side of toasty garlic bread. Get ready for a meal as satisfying as it is delicious.
